d-image:url(&#x27;/water-tech-bg.png&#x27;)"></div><div class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="mb-14 text-center md:mb-20"><h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl" style="color:#90caf9;opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)">Nos Prestations</h2><div class="mx-auto mt-4 h-1 w-20 origin-center rounded-full" style="background-color:#1976d2;transform:scaleX(0)"></div><p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-2xl text-base text-blue-200/70 md:text-lg" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(10px)">Des solutions professionnelles pour l&#x27;entretien et la maintenance de vos réseaux d&#x27;assainissement.</p></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 md:gap-8"><div style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)"><div class="group relative h-full cursor-default overflow-hidden rounded-2xl transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-105"><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-125" style="background-image:url(&#x27;/svc-debouchage.png&#x27;)"></div><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/80 via-black/60 to-black/40 transition-all duration-500 group-hover:from-black/60 group-hover:via-black/40 group-hover:to-black/20"></div><div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center px-6 py-10 text-center"><div class="mb-5 flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#1976d2] transition-all duration-500 group-hover:bg-white"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-droplets h-8 w-8 text-white transition-all duration-500 group-hover:text-[#1976d2]" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M7 16.3c2.2 0 4-1.83 4-4.05 0-1.16-.57-2.26-1.71-3.19S7.29 6.75 7 5.3c-.29 1.45-1.14 2.84-2.29 3.76S3 11.1 3 12.25c0 2.22 1.8 4.05 4 4.05z"></path><path d="M12.56 6.6A10.97 10.97 0 0 0 14 3.02c.5 2.5 2 4.9 4 6.5s3 3.5 3 5.5a6.98 6.98 0 0 1-11.91 4.97"></path></svg></div><h3 class="mb-3 text-lg font-bold leading-snug text-white md:text-xl">Débouchage et nettoyage de canalisations</h3><p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-blue-100/80 md:text-base">Intervention rapide pour déboucher et nettoyer vos canalisations. Nous éliminons les obstructions les plus tenaces et restaurons un écoulement optimal, quel que soit le diamètre ou le type de réseau.</p></div></div></div><div style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)"><div class="group relative h-full cursor-default overflow-hidden rounded-2xl transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-105"><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-125" style="background-image:url(&#x27;/svc-hydrocurage.png&#x27;)"></div><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/80 via-black/60 to-black/40 transition-all duration-500 group-hover:from-black/60 group-hover:via-black/40 group-hover:to-black/20"></div><div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center px-6 py-10 text-center"><div class="mb-5 flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#1976d2] transition-all duration-500 group-hover:bg-white"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-gauge h-8 w-8 text-white transition-all duration-500 group-hover:text-[#1976d2]" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m12 14 4-4"></path><path d="M3.34 19a10 10 0 1 1 17.32 0"></path></svg></div><h3 class="mb-3 text-lg font-bold leading-snug text-white md:text-xl">Hydrocurage haute pression</h3><p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-blue-100/80 md:text-base">Nettoyage en profondeur par camion haute pression jusqu&#x27;à 200 bars. L&#x27;hydrocurage élimine tartre, graisses, boues et racines pour redonner toute sa capacité à vos canalisations.</p></div></div></div><div style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)"><div class="group relative h-full cursor-default overflow-hidden rounded-2xl transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-105"><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-125" style="background-image:url(&#x27;/svc-curage.png&#x27;)"></div><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/80 via-black/60 to-black/40 transition-all duration-500 group-hover:from-black/60 group-hover:via-black/40 group-hover:to-black/20"></div><div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center px-6 py-10 text-center"><div class="mb-5 flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#1976d2] transition-all duration-500 group-hover:bg-white"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-waves h-8 w-8 text-white transition-all duration-500 group-hover:text-[#1976d2]" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2 6c.6.5 1.2 1 2.5 1C7 7 7 5 9.5 5c2.6 0 2.4 2 5 2 2.5 0 2.5-2 5-2 1.3 0 1.9.5 2.5 1"></path><path d="M2 12c.6.5 1.2 1 2.5 1 2.5 0 2.5-2 5-2 2.6 0 2.4 2 5 2 2.5 0 2.5-2 5-2 1.3 0 1.9.5 2.5 1"></path><path d="M2 18c.6.5 1.2 1 2.5 1 2.5 0 2.5-2 5-2 2.6 0 2.4 2 5 2 2.5 0 2.5-2 5-2 1.3 0 1.9.5 2.5 1"></path></svg></div><h3 class="mb-3 text-lg font-bold leading-snug text-white md:text-xl">Curage réseaux EU/EP</h3><p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-blue-100/80 md:text-base">Curage spécialisé des réseaux d&#x27;eaux usées (EU) et eaux pluviales (EP). Nous assurons l&#x27;entretien complet de vos collecteurs, regard et ouvrages pour prévenir les inondations et les pollutions.</p></div></div></div><div style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)"><div class="group relative h-full cursor-default overflow-hidden rounded-2xl transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-105"><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-125" style="background-image:url(&#x27;/pipe-inspection-cam.png&#x27;)"></div><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/80 via-black/60 to-black/40 transition-all duration-500 group-hover:from-black/60 group-hover:via-black/40 group-hover:to-black/20"></div><div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center px-6 py-10 text-center"><div class="mb-5 flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#1976d2] transition-all duration-500 group-hover:bg-white"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-camera h-8 w-8 text-white transition-all duration-500 group-hover:text-[#1976d2]" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M14.5 4h-5L7 7H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v9a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V9a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-3l-2.5-3z"></path><circle cx="12" cy="13" r="3"></circle></svg></div><h3 class="mb-3 text-lg font-bold leading-snug text-white md:text-xl">Inspection caméra</h3><p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-blue-100/80 md:text-base">Diagnostic de précision par inspection vidéo de vos canalisations. Nos caméras HD repèrent fissures, déformations et intrusions. Un rapport vidéo détaillé vous est remis après chaque intervention.</p></div></div></div><div style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)"><div class="group relative h-full cursor-default overflow-hidden rounded-2xl transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-105"><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-125" style="background-image:url(&#x27;/svc-pompage.png&#x27;)"></div><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/80 via-black/60 to-black/40 transition-all duration-500 group-hover:from-black/60 group-hover:via-black/40 group-hover:to-black/20"></div><div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center px-6 py-10 text-center"><div class="mb-5 flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#1976d2] transition-all duration-500 group-hover:bg-white"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-truck h-8 w-8 text-white transition-all duration-500 group-hover:text-[#1976d2]" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M14 18V6a2 2 0 0 0-2-2H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v11a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h2"></path><path d="M15 18H9"></path><path d="M19 18h2a1 1 0 0 0 1-1v-3.65a1 1 0 0 0-.22-.624l-3.48-4.35A1 1 0 0 0 17.52 8H14"></path><circle cx="17" cy="18" r="2"></circle><circle cx="7" cy="18" r="2"></circle></svg></div><h3 class="mb-3 text-lg font-bold leading-snug text-white md:text-xl">Pompage</h3><p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-blue-100/80 md:text-base">Service de pompage complet : fosses septiques, bacs à graisses, puisards et regards. Vidange, curage et traitement des effluents dans le respect des normes environnementales en vigueur.</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="inspection-camera" class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-white relative overflow-hidden"><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat opacity-10" style="background-image:url(&#x27;/fiber-optic-bg.png&#x27;)"></div><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-white/95"></div><div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center"><div class="order-2 lg:order-1 relative" style="opacity:0;transform:translateX(-50px)"><div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-500"><img alt="Inspection caméra haute définition HYDREX - caméra d&#x27;inspection dans canalisation" loading="lazy" width="640" height="480" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="w-full h-auto object-cover" style="color:transparent" src="/pipe-inspection-cam.png"/><div class="absolute top-4 left-4 bg-[#0a2540]/90 backdrop-blur-sm text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg flex items-center gap-2"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-camera w-5 h-5 text-[#42a5f5]" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M14.5 4h-5L7 7H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v9a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V9a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-3l-2.5-3z"></path><circle cx="12" cy="13" r="3"></circle></svg><span class="text-sm font-semibold">Technologie 4K</span></div></div><div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 w-32 h-32 bg-[#e3f2fd] rounded-2xl -z-10"></div></div><div class="order-1 lg:order-2" style="opacity:0;transform:translateX(50px)"><h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-[#0a2540] mb-2">Inspection Caméra</h2><p class="text-xl text-[#0d47a1] font-medium mb-6">Diagnostic de précision</p><div class="space-y-4 text-[#0a2540]/80 leading-relaxed mb-8"><p>Notre service d&#x27;inspection par caméra offre un<!-- --> <strong class="text-[#0a2540]">diagnostic de précision avant intervention</strong>, permettant d&#x27;identifier exactement la nature et la localisation du problème sans travaux inutiles.</p><p>Grâce au <strong class="text-[#0a2540]">rendu visuel HD</strong>, vous bénéficiez d&#x27;un contrôle complet de l&#x27;état de vos canalisations. Chaque inspection donne lieu à des <strong class="text-[#0a2540]">rapports détaillés avec vidéos et photos</strong>, parfaits pour un suivi dans le temps.</p><p>Notre technologie permet la<!-- --> <strong class="text-[#0a2540]">détection de fissures, racines, effondrements</strong> <!-- -->et tout autre défaut structurel avec une précision inégalée.</p></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3 mb-8" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)"><div class="flex items-center gap-3" style="opacity:0;transform:translateX(-20px)"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle-check-big w-5 h-5 text-[#1976d2] flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21.801 10A10 10 0 1 1 17 3.335"></path><path d="m9 11 3 3L22 4"></path></svg><span class="text-[#0a2540] font-medium">Caméra HD 4K</span></div><div class="flex items-center gap-3" style="opacity:0;transform:translateX(-20px)"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle-check-big w-5 h-5 text-[#1976d2] flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21.801 10A10 10 0 1 1 17 3.335"></path><path d="m9 11 3 3L22 4"></path></svg><span class="text-[#0a2540] font-medium">Rapport vidéo complet</span></div><div class="flex items-center gap-3" style="opacity:0;transform:translateX(-20px)"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle-check-big w-5 h-5 text-[#1976d2] flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21.801 10A10 10 0 1 1 17 3.335"></path><path d="m9 11 3 3L22 4"></path></svg><span class="text-[#0a2540] font-medium">Diagnostic en temps réel</span></div><div class="flex items-center gap-3" style="opacity:0;transform:translateX(-20px)"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle-check-big w-5 h-5 text-[#1976d2] flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21.801 10A10 10 0 1 1 17 3.335"></path><path d="m9 11 3 3L22 4"></path></svg><span class="text-[#0a2540] font-medium">Conseils de réparation</span></div></div><a href="#contact" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-[#0d47a1] hover:bg-[#0a2540] text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-xl transition-colors shadow-lg shadow-[#0d47a1]/20" tabindex="0" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-camera w-5 h-5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M14.5 4h-5L7 7H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v9a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V9a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-3l-2.5-3z"></path><circle cx="12" cy="13" r="3"></circle></svg>Demander une inspection</a></div></div></div></section><section id="professionnels" class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-[#f5f9ff] relative overflow-hidden"><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat opacity-[0.08]" style="background-image:url(&#x27;/pro-kitchen-detail.png&#x27;);filter:blur(2px)"></div><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#f5f9ff]/95"></div><div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center"><div style="opacity:0;transform:translateX(-50px)"><h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-[#0a2540] mb-2">Professionnels &amp; Restaurants</h2><p class="text-xl text-[#0d47a1] font-medium mb-6">Une réactivité absolue pour votre activité</p><div class="space-y-4 text-[#0a2540]/80 leading-relaxed mb-10"><p>HYDREX accompagne les professionnels avec des programmes de<!-- --> <strong class="text-[#0a2540]">maintenance préventive planifiée</strong>, adaptés au rythme de votre activité. Nous anticipons les problèmes avant qu&#x27;ils ne surviennent.</p><p>Spécialistes de la <strong class="text-[#0a2540]">gestion des graisses et des fosses</strong>, nous assurons le bon fonctionnement de vos installations sanitaires et de vos réseaux d&#x27;évacuation, conformément aux normes en vigueur.</p><p>Notre <strong class="text-[#0a2540]">réactivité absolue</strong> et nos protocoles préventifs limitent drastiquement les risques d&#x27;immobilisation de votre établissement. Et grâce à nos<!-- --> <strong class="text-[#0a2540]">contrats d&#x27;entretien personnalisés</strong>, vous bénéficiez d&#x27;un suivi sur mesure à tarif préférentiel.</p></div><div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-10" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)"><div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-4 sm:p-5 text-center shadow-md border border-[#e3f2fd]" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-clock w-6 h-6 text-[#1976d2] mx-auto mb-2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 6v6l4 2"></path><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg><p class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-[#0a2540]">24/7</p><p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-[#0a2540]/70 font-medium mt-1">Disponibilité</p></div><div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-4 sm:p-5 text-center shadow-md border border-[#e3f2fd]" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-shield w-6 h-6 text-[#1976d2] mx-auto mb-2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z"></path></svg><p class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-[#0a2540]">&lt;2h</p><p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-[#0a2540]/70 font-medium mt-1">Temps d&#x27;intervention</p></div><div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-4 sm:p-5 text-center shadow-md border border-[#e3f2fd]" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-thumbs-up w-6 h-6 text-[#1976d2] mx-auto mb-2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M7 10v12"></path><path d="M15 5.88 14 10h5.83a2 2 0 0 1 1.92 2.56l-2.33 8A2 2 0 0 1 17.5 22H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2.76a2 2 0 0 0 1.79-1.11L12 2a3.13 3.13 0 0 1 3 3.88Z"></path></svg><p class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-[#0a2540]">100%</p><p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-[#0a2540]/70 font-medium mt-1">Satisfaction</p></div></div><a href="#contact" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-[#0d47a1] hover:bg-[#0a2540] text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-xl transition-colors shadow-lg shadow-[#0d47a1]/20" tabindex="0" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-building2 lucide-building-2 w-5 h-5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 22V4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h8a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v18Z"></path><path d="M6 12H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h2"></path><path d="M18 9h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v9a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-2"></path><path d="M10 6h4"></path><path d="M10 10h4"></path><path d="M10 14h4"></path><path d="M10 18h4"></path></svg>Obtenir un contrat d&#x27;entretien</a></div><div class="relative" style="opacity:0;transform:translateX(50px)"><div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl"><img alt="Canalisations propres dans une cuisine professionnelle entretenue par HYDREX" loading="lazy" width="640" height="480" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="w-full h-auto object-cover" style="color:transparent" src="/clean-kitchen-pipes.png"/><div class="absolute bottom-4 right-4 bg-[#0a2540]/90 backdrop-blur-sm text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg flex items-center gap-2"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-clock w-5 h-5 text-[#42a5f5]" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 6v6l4 2"></path><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg><span class="text-sm font-semibold">Intervention &lt; 2h</span></div></div><div class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 w-32 h-32 bg-[#e3f2fd] rounded-2xl -z-10"></div></div></div></div></section><section id="zone-intervention" class="py-20 md:py-28 relative overflow-hidden"><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat opacity-[0.05]" style="background-image:url(&#x27;/water-tech-bg.png&#x27;)"></div><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#f5f9ff] via-white to-[#f0f4ff]"></div><div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10"><div class="text-center mb-14" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)"><p class="text-[#1976d2] font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-3" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(15px)">Couverture géographique</p><h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-[#0a2540] mb-3">Zone d&#x27;Intervention</h2><p class="text-xl text-[#0d47a1] font-medium max-w-2xl mx-auto">Une présence locale, une couverture nationale</p></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 lg:gap-16 items-center" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)"><div class="relative" style="opacity:0;transform:translateX(-40px)"><div class="rounded-2xl p-4 sm:p-6 md:p-8"><div class="relative w-full aspect-[449/506]"><img src="/france-map.png" alt="Carte de France" class="w-full h-auto select-none contrast-[2.5]" draggable="false"/><div class="absolute cursor-pointer" style="left:56%;top:84%;transform:translate(-50%, -50%)"><div class="absolute rounded-full transition-all duration-500 ease-out bg-[#1976d2]/10 scale-[2]" style="width:10px;height:10px;top:50%;left:50%;margin-top:-5px;margin-left:-5px"></div><div class="relative z-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full transition-all duration-300 ease-out w-6 h-6 bg-[#1976d2] shadow-md shadow-[#1976d2]/25"><span class="text-white font-bold select-none transition-all duration-300 text-[9px]">66</span></div></div><div class="absolute cursor-pointer" style="left:57%;top:77%;transform:translate(-50%, -50%)"><div class="absolute rounded-full transition-all duration-500 ease-out bg-[#1976d2]/10 scale-[2]" style="width:10px;height:10px;top:50%;left:50%;margin-top:-5px;margin-left:-5px"></div><div class="relative z-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full transition-all duration-300 ease-out w-6 h-6 bg-[#1976d2] shadow-md shadow-[#1976d2]/25"><span class="text-white font-bold select-none transition-all duration-300 text-[9px]">11</span></div></div><div class="absolute cursor-pointer" style="left:62%;top:79%;transform:translate(-50%, -50%)"><div class="absolute rounded-full transition-all duration-500 ease-out bg-[#1976d2]/10 scale-[2]" style="width:10px;height:10px;top:50%;left:50%;margin-top:-5px;margin-left:-5px"></div><div class="relative z-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full transition-all duration-300 ease-out w-6 h-6 bg-[#1976d2] shadow-md shadow-[#1976d2]/25"><span class="text-white font-bold select-none transition-all duration-300 text-[9px]">34</span></div></div><div class="absolute cursor-pointer" style="left:65%;top:75%;transform:translate(-50%, -50%)"><div class="absolute rounded-full transition-all duration-500 ease-out bg-[#1976d2]/10 scale-[2]" style="width:10px;height:10px;top:50%;left:50%;margin-top:-5px;margin-left:-5px"></div><div class="relative z-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full transition-all duration-300 ease-out w-6 h-6 bg-[#1976d2] shadow-md shadow-[#1976d2]/25"><span class="text-white font-bold select-none transition-all duration-300 text-[9px]">30</span></div></div><div class="absolute cursor-pointer" style="left:67%;top:70%;transform:translate(-50%, -50%)"><div class="absolute rounded-full transition-all duration-500 ease-out bg-[#1976d2]/10 scale-[2]" style="width:10px;height:10px;top:50%;left:50%;margin-top:-5px;margin-left:-5px"></div><div class="relative z-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full transition-all duration-300 ease-out w-6 h-6 bg-[#1976d2] shadow-md shadow-[#1976d2]/25"><span class="text-white font-bold select-none transition-all duration-300 text-[9px]">84</span></div></div><div class="absolute cursor-pointer" style="left:69%;top:78%;transform:translate(-50%, -50%)"><div class="absolute rounded-full transition-all duration-500 ease-out bg-[#1976d2]/10 scale-[2]" style="width:10px;height:10px;top:50%;left:50%;margin-top:-5px;margin-left:-5px"></div><div class="relative z-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full transition-all duration-300 ease-out w-6 h-6 bg-[#1976d2] shadow-md shadow-[#1976d2]/25"><span class="text-white font-bold select-none transition-all duration-300 text-[9px]">13</span></div></div></div></div><div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-5 mt-2 text-[11px] text-[#0a2540]/50"><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5"><div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-[#1976d2]"></div><span>Départements couverts</span></div><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5"><div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-[#42a5f5] shadow-sm shadow-[#42a5f5]/50"></div><span>Survolez pour découvrir</span></div></div></div><div class="flex flex-col gap-7" style="opacity:0;transform:translateX(40px)"><div><h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0a2540] mb-4">Notre zone d&#x27;intervention principale</h3><p class="text-[#0a2540]/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">HYDREX est implanté au cœur du <strong class="text-[#0a2540]">sud de la France</strong>, avec une couverture dédiée des départements de l&#x27;Hérault (34), du Gard (30), du Vaucluse (84), de l&#x27;Aude (11), des Pyrénées-Orientales (66) et des Bouches-du-Rhône (13).</p><p class="text-[#0a2540]/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">Notre <strong class="text-[#0a2540]">proximité géographique</strong> avec les grandes agglomérations — Montpellier, Nîmes, Avignon, Carcassonne, Perpignan et Marseille — nous permet d&#x27;intervenir rapidement sur l&#x27;ensemble de la région Occitanie et PACA.</p><p class="text-[#0a2540]/80 leading-relaxed">Nos équipes connaissent parfaitement les <strong class="text-[#0a2540]">réseaux d&#x27;assainissement locaux</strong>, les réglementations en vigueur et les spécificités de chaque commune pour vous garantir un service adapté et réactif.</p></div><div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3"><div class="flex items-start gap-3 bg-white rounded-xl p-4 shadow-sm border border-[#e3f2fd] hover:shadow-md transition-shadow"><div class="w-9 h-9 rounded-lg bg-[#e3f2fd] flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-clock w-4 h-4 text-[#1976d2]" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 6v6l4 2"></path><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg></div><div><p class="font-semibold text-[#0a2540] text-sm">Intervention rapide</p><p class="text-[#0a2540]/60 text-xs">Sur place en moins de 2h</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 bg-white rounded-xl p-4 shadow-sm border border-[#e3f2fd] hover:shadow-md transition-shadow"><div class="w-9 h-9 rounded-lg bg-[#e3f2fd] flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-shield w-4 h-4 text-[#1976d2]" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z"></path></svg></div><div><p class="font-semibold text-[#0a2540] text-sm">Expertise locale</p><p class="text-[#0a2540]/60 text-xs">Connaissance des réseaux</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 bg-white rounded-xl p-4 shadow-sm border border-[#e3f2fd] hover:shadow-md transition-shadow"><div class="w-9 h-9 rounded-lg bg-[#e3f2fd] flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-truck w-4 h-4 text-[#1976d2]" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M14 18V6a2 2 0 0 0-2-2H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v11a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h2"></path><path d="M15 18H9"></path><path d="M19 18h2a1 1 0 0 0 1-1v-3.65a1 1 0 0 0-.22-.624l-3.48-4.35A1 1 0 0 0 17.52 8H14"></path><circle cx="17" cy="18" r="2"></circle><circle cx="7" cy="18" r="2"></circle></svg></div><div><p class="font-semibold text-[#0a2540] text-sm">Équipements mobiles</p><p class="text-[#0a2540]/60 text-xs">Camions haute pression</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 bg-white rounded-xl p-4 shadow-sm border border-[#e3f2fd] hover:shadow-md transition-shadow"><div class="w-9 h-9 rounded-lg bg-[#e3f2fd] flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-map-pin w-4 h-4 text-[#1976d2]" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 10c0 4.993-5.539 10.193-7.399 11.799a1 1 0 0 1-1.202 0C9.539 20.193 4 14.993 4 10a8 8 0 0 1 16 0"></path><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"></circle></svg></div><div><p class="font-semibold text-[#0a2540] text-sm">6 départements</p><p class="text-[#0a2540]/60 text-xs">Occitanie &amp; PACA</p></div></div></div><div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#0a2540] to-[#0d47a1] rounded-2xl p-6 text-white relative overflow-hidden"><div class="absolute -top-10 -right-10 w-32 h-32 bg-[#42a5f5]/10 rounded-full blur-2xl"></div><div class="relative flex items-start gap-4"><div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-xl bg-white/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-globe w-6 h-6 text-[#42a5f5]" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><path d="M12 2a14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0 20 14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0-20"></path><path d="M2 12h20"></path></svg></div><div><p class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Intervention sur toute la France</p><p class="text-white/70 text-sm leading-relaxed">Au-delà de notre zone principale, HYDREX se déplace sur l&#x27;ensemble du territoire français pour des interventions spécifiques ou des contrats d&#x27;entretien. Nos camions haute pression et nos équipes qualifiées sont prêts à intervenir où que vous soyez.</p></div></div></div><a href="#contact" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-[#0d47a1] hover:bg-[#0a2540] text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3.5 rounded-xl transition-colors shadow-lg shadow-[#0d47a1]/20 group"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-phone w-4 h-4" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M13.832 16.568a1 1 0 0 0 1.213-.303l.355-.465A2 2 0 0 1 17 15h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v3a2 2 0 0 1-2 2A18 18 0 0 1 2 4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v3a2 2 0 0 1-.8 1.6l-.468.351a1 1 0 0 0-.292 1.233 14 14 0 0 0 6.392 6.384"></path></svg>Demander un devis gratuit<span class="group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">→</span></a></div></div></div></section><section id="contact" class="relative py-20 overflow-hidden"><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat opacity-[0.06]" style="background-image:url(&#x27;/water-tech-bg.png&#x27;)"></div><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#f5f9ff] via-white to-[#f0f4ff]"></div><div class="relative container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="text-center mb-14" style="opacity:0;transform